      "type": "text",
      "text": {
        "content": "<p><em>Unknown to almost everyone in the Roman Empire, a hidden war rages on the shores of Britannia. Ancient and alien gods have broken free from prisons, with human worshippers seeking to curry favor. Human soldiers face shattered minds as much as broken bodies. The misty island province is the front line of the Shadow War.</em></p><p><em>Refer to the Britannia & Beyond rulebook for full details.</em></p>",
